# -*-cperl-*-

=head1 NAME

_SCUBA2_PCA_TIDY_ - delete files created as part of PCA on SCUBA-2 data

=head1 SYNOPSIS

_SCUBA2_PCA_TIDY_

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive deletes files created during the PCA analysis on
SCUBA-2 data. The recipe parameter C<PCA_KEEPFILES> is used to
determine whether or not the output files are deleted. The copies made
of the raw data are always deleted.

=head1 ARGUMENTS

The are no arguments.

=head1 EXTERNAL TASKS

The following external task is used:

=over 2

=item ORAC-DR PRIMITIVES:

_DELETE_TEMP_FILES_

=back

=head1 NOTES

This primitive is for use with SCUBA-2 data only.

=head1 OUTPUT DATA

None.

=head1 OUTPUT FILES

None.

